metadata.name: The Coffeehouse
metadata.description:
The Coffeehouse – a place where ideas, scientific theories, and artistic projects were once discussed. The coffeehouses have played a key role in shaping the Viennese culture. Now, some are being closed and standing empty, each full of history.

Includes a signed fine-art print.

Taken on 35mm film.
Vienna, Austria.
